42.original_subtitle: If you're familiar with Electron, Tori is like Electron

43.original_subtitle: By the way, writing pure JavaScript is basically Rust first
43.translated_subtitle: 顺便说一下，写纯JavaScript基本上是先写Rust代码

44.original_subtitle: But then you can use any front-end framework JavaScript that you want
44.translated_subtitle: 但之后你可以使用任何你想要的前端框架JavaScript

45.original_subtitle: You can use Svelte, React, etc.

46.original_subtitle: And that's how you can easily build cross-platform applications
46.translated_subtitle: 这就是你可以轻松构建跨平台应用程序的方法

47.original_subtitle: And in the future, even mobile apps I think
47.translated_subtitle: 我认为将来甚至可以是移动应用程序

48.original_subtitle: And the major difference between Tori and Electron

49.original_subtitle: is that Electron ships the entire Chrome browser or whatever
49.translated_subtitle: 是Electron携带了整个Chrome浏览器或其他

50.original_subtitle: but Tori, on the other hand, uses the built-in web views in your operating system
50.translated_subtitle: 但Tori，另一方面，使用的是操作系统内置的web视图

51.original_subtitle: So your operating system Windows, Mac OS, Linux, etc.
51.translated_subtitle: 所以你的操作系统可能是Windows、Mac OS、Linux等等。

52.original_subtitle: have a built-in browser that comes with it, right?
52.translated_subtitle: 都自带一个浏览器，对吧？

53.translated_subtitle: 所以它使用的是那个自带的浏览器。

54.original_subtitle: That's basically how I understand it.
54.translated_subtitle: 基本上，我是这么理解的。

55.original_subtitle: But because Tori is so new, it doesn't really have that entire ecosystem that Electron does.
55.translated_subtitle: 不过，由于Tori还很新，它没有Electron那样完整的生态系统。

56.original_subtitle: And keep in mind, Tori isn't this Electron killer that people pretend it is.
56.translated_subtitle: 请记住，Tori并不是大家说的那个Electron杀手。

57.original_subtitle: Because you're going to have to write Rust, etc., which is, of course, the blazing fast language.
57.translated_subtitle: 因为你需要用Rust等语言来编写，这当然是一种极快的语言。

58.original_subtitle: So if you're into that, then you can use Tori.
58.translated_subtitle: 所以如果你对这个有兴趣，可以用Tori。

59.original_subtitle: And of course, it uses Svelte for the UI and Tailwind CSS for the styling.
59.translated_subtitle: 当然，它用Svelte来做UI，用Tailwind CSS来做样式。

60.original_subtitle: But in particular, it uses Shad C and Svelte.
